  "body": "## Issue\r\n\r\nNow that PRs #4420 and #4365 have been merged, the `translateJsonToSolidity` and `resolveVyperModules` resolver options are a redundant mechanism.\r\n\r\nThese options should be removed, and the checks that switch on them should instead look at the compiler version that was passed (`translateJsonToSolidity` should become, are we using Solidity, and `resolveVyperModules` should become, are we using Vyper).\r\n\r\nMoreover, any code that passes these options in should changed back so that it no longer does so.\r\n\r\n## Environment\r\n\r\n* Truffle version (`truffle version`): 5.4.23",
